{
  "stem": "26142.16",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived in Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we came to the camp, I saw a big sign, [SPEAKING GERMAN], I thought that we-- we are going to be treated like war prisoners.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It won't be so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they opened the gates, a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] German officer, the Lagerkommandant, I think he was, the Hungarians reported that they brought 800 Jews and they-- they started counting.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, the merchandise has to-- has to check out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would count-- you know, that's why they put us in fours-- and they would count how many people we are.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got thrown into a-- to a big room, a big hall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We came into this big hall and-- and we saw-- we started seeing people that were dressed in those striped uniforms-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this is vertical stripes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the back of their-- of their jackets was a-- a K slash L.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So then we realized that the KL in German means konzentrationslager.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is not a prisoner of war camp, but it was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The-- the-- the-- The people in-- in that-- in that had-- you couldn't-- you couldn't see a normal look on their face.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It-- it was just like-- like in-- in a crazy house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You-- you could see some of these people, they had some haircuts that was going like this, just cut through, and some of them, just the other-- the other way around.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And some of-- some of them-- some, you heard all kinds of languages besides German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was all kinds of languages-- Polish, Greek, Italian, all kinds of-- And-- and the people were mostly you could see just holes, the eyes sticking out.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
